@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_olsnha(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (((tmp + 0.46 * v0 + 0.41) / wp.abs(v2 + 0.47)) / 0.72)
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.cos((tmp + 0.82 * v0 + 0.38)))
    tmp = (wp.exp(0.59) - wp.exp((v2 + 0.94 + v1 + 0.14)))
    v2 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.64) + (v1 + 0.82 + v1 + 0.21)) * (v1 * wp.cos(v2 + 0.62)))
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.sin((v2 + 0.23 - v2 + 0.91)))
    tmp = 0.25
    v0 = wp.abs(wp.sin((tmp + 0.12 + v2 + 0.89)))
    data[tid] = v0
